Leverage AWS internal network to route to your app (route through edge locations)

Works with Elastic IP, EC2 instances, ALB, NLB, public or private

Consistent Perf:
	- Intelligent routing to lowest latency and fast regional failover
	- No issue with client cache (IP doesn't change (Anycast IP))
	- Internal AWS network

Health Checks:
	- Global Acce perfs a health check of your app
	- helps make app global (failover < 1 min for unhealthy)
	- great for DR (Disaster Recovery)

Security:
	- only 2 external IP need to be whitelisted
	- DDoS protection thanks to AWS Shield